Instale o python anaconda (testado: python 3.7)
Crie um ambiente conda
Instale o pip
Instale o tensorflow (2.8.0 é a versão testada) usando o pip:
	pip install tensorflow==2.8.0
Instale o opentsne:
	conda install opentsne
Instale o pandas:
	conda install pandas
	conda install pandas-datareader
Instale o pillow:
	conda install pillow
Instale o dash:
	conda install -c conda-forge dash-html-components
	pip install dash==2.2.0
Instale o matplotlib
	pip install matplotlib
Instale o sklearn
	pip install -U scikit-learn
Downgrade werkzeug to 2.0.3
Downgrade flask to 2.1.3
conda install -c conda-forge dash-bootstrap-components=1.2.1
